Open source photo stitching software library
http://www.panoramatools.com/

Tutorial for scripting with PanoramaTools:
http://wiki.panotools.org/Panorama_scripting_in_a_nutshell

Hugin (A graphical tool/editor for panoramas, based on panoramatools), GPL and available for Linux, Mac and Windows:
http://hugin.sourceforge.net/


